name: CrossoverMix
description:
Hi there, and welcome to my first ever checkpoint!

What I decided to do with this is create an illusionary combination of Western cartoon and anime styles, and also add 3D photorealism to the mix. It's something that I personally like to call:

CrossoverMix.

Recipe (and I credit everyone who made these models):

0.55(0.6(toonyouB31.MGIm) + 0.4(AnythingV5)) + 0.45(realisticVisionV20_v20) + 0.7(revAnimated_v122 - lyriel_v15)

(v2.0 update) - Added epicRealism - pure Evolution and AbsoluteReality into the mix to make the model to enhance the realism, lighting, and shadows to my subjects.

Recommended samplers: Euler A, or DPM++ 2M Karras

Clip skip: 2

CFG Scale: 5-7

Upscale by: 2

Denoising strength: (if you're doing hires. fix, do ~0.55-0.7)

I didn't bake any VAE in, but I highly recommend these VAEs:

vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

Night Sky VAE (located at the download link)

Suggestions and feedback are welcome! Hope you enjoy!
